  }, {
    "tStartMs": 58792,
    "dDurationMs": 1869,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-Ohh."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 60661,
    "dDurationMs": 1935,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-Then Bondi was like,\n\"So you want me to arrest NATO,"
